Package: EvoR
Title: An R Interface for the Evo2 Genomic Foundation Model
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Himanshu", family = "Bhandary", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "2032ushimanshu@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-9859-3934", affiliation = "BDB-Genomics"))
Description: Provides a lightweight R interface for the Evo2 genomic foundation 
    model via the NVIDIA BioNeMo API. This package supports three core 
    modalities: biological sequence generation, log-likelihood scoring for 
    Variant Effect Prediction (VEP), and high-dimensional sequence embeddings 
    for downstream regulatory pattern recognition. Designed for research in 
    epigenomics and Type 2 Diabetes (T2D).
